47
00:01:43,033 --> 00:01:45,400
(Making noodles)
I've done this with my clothes before

48
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:46,800
(Making noodles)
but it's first time doing it on my shoes.

49
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,500
Well, as for me,

50
00:01:48,500 --> 00:01:50,700
(//Shy//)
I've done both before.

51
00:01:50,700 --> 00:01:53,067
When I was little, I was bored...

52
00:01:53,067 --> 00:01:54,667
(Haha)

53
00:01:54,667 --> 00:01:56,567
(Kneading)

54
