69
00:02:29,067 --> 00:02:30,233
Well...

70
00:02:30,233 --> 00:02:33,700
(Taking caffeine for inspiration)

71
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:35,233
Oh, ARNO Hyung...

72
00:02:35,233 --> 00:02:35,667
That's really~

73
