I'm just winging it.

95
00:03:07,567 --> 00:03:08,733
(I'm smiling, but not really smiling)

96
00:03:08,733 --> 00:03:10,167
ANXIN is that kind of guy.

97
00:03:10,167 --> 00:03:10,633
Just...

98
