102
00:03:20,667 --> 00:03:23,067
OK! I'll peel off the tape now.

103
00:03:25,267 --> 00:03:27,867
(Peel off the glove first)

104
00:03:27,867 --> 00:03:31,367
Once I peel off the tape,
I'll move on to a really important...

105
00:03:32,167 --> 00:03:33,733
Step after that.

106
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:38,133
That's my shoes'

107
00:03:38,133 --> 00:03:39,067
That's my shoes' SOUL.

108
00:03:39,067 --> 00:03:43,200
(What that 'important step' will be?)

109
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:44,433
What?

110
00:03:44,433 --> 00:03:47,200
I don't know how to bring my idea to life.

111
00:03:47,200 --> 00:03:48,367
It's kind of...

112
00:03:48,367 --> 00:03:49,367
It's kind of... Street!

113
00:03:49,367 --> 00:03:50,533
