A street vibe.

114
00:03:50,533 --> 00:03:51,767
You can use this sandpaper, you know?

115
00:03:51,767 --> 00:03:53,200
(Sandpaper?)
To make it like this...

116
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,433
(Shows the sandpaper to help him understand)

117
00:03:54,433 --> 00:03:55,400
Oh, I like that.

118
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,667
(Using sandpaper & scissors)

119
00:03:56,667 --> 00:04:00,167
'I'll move on to a really important step...'

120
00:04:00,167 --> 00:04:03,533
(The scratching sound
echoes through the quiet studio)

121
