Or making it show my toes?

125
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:14,633
(Advice)
Then, turn them into slippers.

126
00:04:14,633 --> 00:04:16,700
Slippers~
(Superior breathability)

127
00:04:16,700 --> 00:04:20,667
Oh, JUNSEO Hyung gave me some socks as a gift.

128
00:04:20,667 --> 00:04:25,100
(Might as well make it look good)
I'll wear the jewel socks that show my toes.

129
00:04:25,100 --> 00:04:27,633
I tried to write a comment here.

130
00:04:27,633 --> 00:04:28,833
"The Coolest"

131
