But shoes like that already exist.

132
00:04:31,067 --> 00:04:32,900
I'll go with 'The coolest.'

133
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:34,333
The coolest sneakers.

134
00:04:34,333 --> 00:04:34,967
By any chance...

135
00:04:34,967 --> 00:04:36,867
Is there anyone here

136
00:04:36,867 --> 00:04:38,700
(First come, first served: 1 spot only)
who wants to go outside with me?

137
00:04:38,700 --> 00:04:39,967
