140
00:04:44,433 --> 00:04:46,700
Can't you get the feel you're going for?

141
00:04:47,267 --> 00:04:48,033
I'm exhausted.

142
00:04:48,033 --> 00:04:50,000
(So tiring)

143
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:53,000
(A street vibe made on the street)

144
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:56,100
Is this right?

145
00:04:56,100 --> 00:04:58,167
(Even a fleeting doubt can't stop his hands)

146
00:04:58,167 --> 00:05:01,300
(Moved to a rougher location)

147
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:04,800
(To pour my soul into it,
I have to do this)

148
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:08,467
