continued for quite some time)

149
00:05:08,467 --> 00:05:11,133
(At the same time, inside the studio)

150
00:05:11,133 --> 00:05:12,100
Teacher!

151
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:13,433
(LONG is back)

152
00:05:13,433 --> 00:05:15,333
(Showing off the footage)
He's really proactive.

153
00:05:15,333 --> 00:05:17,167
You're the first person to go this far.

154
00:05:17,167 --> 00:05:19,467
(Became the first person.)

155
00:05:19,467 --> 00:05:22,433
(Meanwhile, ARNO quietly finished one shoe)

156
00:05:22,433 --> 00:05:26,300
(ANXIN filled his work
with self-love and love for ALD1)

157
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:31,000
Hahaha~

158
00:05:33,467 --> 00:05:35,100
Guys~

159
00:05:35,100 --> 00:05:36,567
(Still tired)

160
00:05:36,567 --> 00:05:38,233
My work!

161
00:05:38,533 --> 00:05:39,400
My work!

162
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,500
My work~

163
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:43,667
I mixed purple, pink, and black

164
00:05:43,667 --> 00:05:46,067
and made it with color as the main focus.

165
00:05:46,067 --> 00:05:49,833
I finished the first one

166
00:05:49,833 --> 00:05:52,000
and the second one...

167
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,567
(Totally drained)
I couldn't make it the same way.

168
00:05:54,567 --> 00:05:57,267
So I made it with a different concept.

169
00:05:58,667 --> 00:06:01,867
(Revealing the palette)

170
00:06:02,667 --> 00:06:03,633
(Announces the 2nd outing)
Let's go!

171
00:06:03,633 --> 00:06:06,367
(Finishes with a burning ritual)

172
00:06:06,367 --> 00:06:09,767
(This is who I am)
Did you even design this part too?

173
00:06:09,767 --> 00:06:10,767
(This is) A street!

174
00:06:11,233 --> 00:06:13,567
Oh, my shoes... My work.

175
00:06:13,567 --> 00:06:15,433
They got a name today.

176
00:06:15,433 --> 00:06:16,367
Just 'Street.'

177
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:20,100
(Meaning of the name)
I walk along the street every day.

178
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:22,233
I dance on the street.

179
00:06:23,167 --> 00:06:26,733
XINLONG ♥ Street

180
00:06:27,467 --> 00:06:29,333
(Laughing on the street)

181
00:06:29,333 --> 00:06:32,367
(Returning)

182
00:06:32,367 --> 00:06:33,467
How do they look?

183
00:06:33,467 --> 00:06:36,167
(I want some compliments)

184
