Did you attach paper and burn it?

185
00:06:37,633 --> 00:06:38,267
Yes.

186
00:06:38,267 --> 00:06:38,933
Amazing~

187
00:06:38,933 --> 00:06:40,633
If I didn't attach paper,

188
00:06:40,633 --> 00:06:42,967
