189
00:06:42,967 --> 00:06:44,200
So, just a bit...

190
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,033
The soot wouldn't have spread like this.

191
00:06:45,033 --> 00:06:45,733
Not the vibe you wanted?

192
00:06:45,733 --> 00:06:48,333
(Impressed teacher)

193
00:06:48,333 --> 00:06:49,433
Did you try that too?

194
00:06:49,433 --> 00:06:50,033
Nope~

195
00:06:50,033 --> 00:06:50,833
Oh, really?

196
00:06:51,333 --> 00:06:52,800
XINLONG is naturally talented.

197
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:53,367
Huh?

198
00:06:53,933 --> 00:06:55,300
(Complimenting XINLONG)
I said it to the camera.

199
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:56,800
Hey, guys~
(XINLONG CAM ON)

200
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,767
I've finished mine too

201
00:06:58,633 --> 00:07:00,567
(Sense of accomplishment)

202
00:07:00,567 --> 00:07:04,567
(Main color)
I made the whole thing black.

203
00:07:04,567 --> 00:07:06,033
The shoelaces are gray!

204
00:07:06,033 --> 00:07:07,433
It's a little different!

205
00:07:07,433 --> 00:07:10,000
Plus, there's a detail
on the surface of the shoelaces.

206
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:12,367
Like they've been slightly torn
with a knife, you know?

207
00:07:12,367 --> 00:07:13,300
You can see it, right?

208
00:07:14,267 --> 00:07:16,233
Wait, ARNO is back.

209
00:07:16,233 --> 00:07:19,167
(ARNO came back
from shooting the final result)

210
00:07:20,200 --> 00:07:21,367
ARNO's left.

211
00:07:21,367 --> 00:07:23,967
The next thing is...
(ARNO is watching)

212
00:07:23,967 --> 00:07:26,433
I put tape on it

213
00:07:26,433 --> 00:07:30,200
to create a scorched look a bit.

214
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:32,367
So I did it outside.
(It was done safely)

215
00:07:33,367 --> 00:07:35,500
Wow, it looks super cool on camera, huh?

216
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:38,600
(Very satisfied)
Wow, it looks really cool on camera.

217
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,967
(ARNO sat down)

218
00:07:39,967 --> 00:07:41,433
ALLYZ!

219
00:07:41,433 --> 00:07:43,333
If you want to try this,

220
00:07:43,333 --> 00:07:44,567
(Like me)
just follow your hunch.

221
00:07:44,567 --> 00:07:47,700
(Positive)
When I started, I didn't expect
that it would turn out like this.

222
00:07:47,700 --> 00:07:50,567
Of course, it's not perfect,

223
00:07:50,567 --> 00:07:52,400
but it turned out better than I expected.

224
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:55,600
(Might as well try on the work of his life)

225
00:07:58,300 --> 00:08:01,200
Oh ♥ Nice, huh?

226
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:03,833
It looks great.
(Watching happy XINLONG is hilarious)

227
00:08:03,833 --> 00:08:05,933
Everyone can tell they're XINLONG's shoes.

228
00:08:05,933 --> 00:08:07,667
(High praise)
10 out of 10.

229
00:08:07,667 --> 00:08:09,700
(Touched for the Nth time)

230
00:08:10,967 --> 00:08:12,033
(High-five)

231
00:08:12,033 --> 00:08:13,267
(Even the teacher agrees)
10! It's really 10 points!

232
00:08:13,267 --> 00:08:13,800
Really?!

233
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,233
Yes.

234
00:08:14,667 --> 00:08:16,433
(In a nutshell)
You're pretty creative.

235
00:08:16,433 --> 00:08:18,100
(Looks like it's his lucky day)

236
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:22,167
(To. ALLYZ)
If you want to copy XINLONG's shoes,

237
00:08:22,167 --> 00:08:24,833
(To. ALLYZ)
your stamina matters more than drawing skills.

238
00:08:24,833 --> 00:08:26,500
Because they have to keep going back and forth?

239
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:27,600
That's kinda true.

240
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:30,133
(ANXIN is in the finishing stage too)

241
00:08:30,133 --> 00:08:31,500
(LONG's Translation Function ON)
What is 'Theme' in Korean?

242
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:31,967
(LONG's Translation Function ON)
'Juje.'

243
00:08:31,967 --> 00:08:33,767
The theme is 'LOVE.'

244
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,300
"I am the best!"

245
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,733
I wrote that kind of comment a lot.

246
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:47,333
I wrote it in Chinese, Korean,
Japanese, and English.
(Self-love written in Nth languages)

247
00:08:47,333 --> 00:08:50,033
And the ALD1 logo on the back.

248
00:08:50,033 --> 00:08:51,400
And here's the key point!

249
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:56,067
I split Chinese pinyin and used it like this.

250
00:08:56,067 --> 00:08:59,467
'The Coolest Sneakers'

251
00:08:59,467 --> 00:09:01,433
('I'm the best' with 'The coolest sneakers')

252
00:09:01,433 --> 00:09:02,667
I love this so much.

253
00:09:02,667 --> 00:09:04,633
'The Coolest Sneakers'

254
00:09:04,633 --> 00:09:06,733
Wow, it's just perfect.

255
00:09:06,733 --> 00:09:08,533
And a key point is here as well.

256
00:09:08,533 --> 00:09:10,833
ANXIN = X

257
00:09:10,833 --> 00:09:12,567
HE XINLONG = L

258
00:09:12,567 --> 00:09:13,767
ZHANG JIAHAO = H

259
00:09:13,767 --> 00:09:15,933
(Not only self-love but brotherly love
inscribed on the shoes)

260
00:09:15,933 --> 00:09:17,700
Today's number one is ANXIN's shoes!

261
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:18,833
(A perfect) 100 points!

262
00:09:18,833 --> 00:09:20,533
10,000 points out of 10.

263
00:09:20,833 --> 00:09:21,367
Sigh~

