00:22:11,633 --> 00:22:14,000
(It's hard to do both with just one mouth)

524
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:17,600
(Cutting it up to share easily)

525
00:22:17,600 --> 00:22:23,767
(Sharing delicious things one by one)

526
00:22:23,767 --> 00:22:25,867
(With the other members)
Let's all come here together.

527
00:22:25,867 --> 00:22:27,500
We'll find even more delicious things

528
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:31,067
(More) and recommend them to the members.

529
00:22:31,067 --> 00:22:33,067
During the fan signing event in Shenzhen,

530
00:22:33,067 --> 00:22:35,400
That legendary beef hot pot.

531
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:37,933
I want to go eat it together.
(ARNO decides to introduce
a gourmet hot pot restaurant in Shenzhen)

532
00:22:37,933 --> 00:22:40,433
Since I came to Korea

533
00:22:40,433 --> 00:22:43,167
(Except for the schedules)
I've only been in Seoul so far.

534
00:22:43,167 --> 00:22:46,200
- Me too
- I've never been to other regions.

535
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,433
How about you, XINLONG?

536
00:22:47,433 --> 00:22:48,967
I've been to many regions,

537
00:22:48,967 --> 00:22:51,200
but I haven't tried the local dishes there.

538
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:55,033
So this time, we're going to Busan
and Daegu, right?

539
00:22:55,033 --> 00:22:58,133
(Looking forward to it)
Let's try the local dishes there too.

540
00:22:58,133 --> 00:22:59,467
(Q. Please tell us about your trainee days too)

541
00:22:59,467 --> 00:23:02,667
The life of a trainee...

542
00:23:02,667 --> 00:23:05,233
As a trainee...
(Trying to recall)

543
00:23:05,233 --> 00:23:06,300
Well...

544
00:23:06,300 --> 00:23:07,267
(Takes a long time to think)

545
00:23:07,267 --> 00:23:08,067
Huh⁉

546
00:23:09,533 --> 00:23:11,233
(Seems difficult)

547
00:23:11,233 --> 00:23:14,567
(To help him out)
When did you become a trainee, Hyung?

548
00:23:14,567 --> 00:23:18,867
I first started at a trainee academy in 2018,

549
00:23:18,867 --> 00:23:21,100
and I first came to Korea in 2020.

550
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:23,167
Did you come alone back then, too?

551
00:23:23,167 --> 00:23:25,533
What did you enjoy most
during your trainee days?

552
00:23:25,533 --> 00:23:26,967
The most fun thing?

553
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:28,500
Clocking out?

554
00:23:28,500 --> 00:23:31,933
(All agreed)

555
00:23:31,933 --> 00:23:35,100
Since it was a tough time...
(Clocking out was the most fun part
during the tough time)

556
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:36,633
But you're happy now!

557
00:23:36,633 --> 00:23:38,833
Precisely because it was so hard...

558
00:23:38,833 --> 00:23:42,867
It led to this happy outcome.
(A happy outcome gained through tough times)

559
00:23:42,867 --> 00:23:44,400
Oh~

560
00:23:44,400 --> 00:23:45,567
Nice comment.

561
00:23:45,567 --> 00:23:50,233
September 25th... No.
(XINLONG also has something to share)

562
00:23:50,233 --> 00:23:52,167
(Anyway) After the finals ended,

563
00:23:52,167 --> 00:23:56,667
we all went out for hot pot
with our families, right?

564
00:23:56,667 --> 00:23:57,633
The three of us?

565
00:23:57,633 --> 00:24:00,000
(CHINYANGZ's family gathering)

566
00:24:00,000 --> 00:24:05,067
At that time, our moms
got to know each other too.

567
00:24:05,067 --> 00:24:07,467
(Since that day)
I feel like we've become closer.

568
00:24:07,467 --> 00:24:09,200
It feels like we've become closer.

569
00:24:09,200 --> 00:24:10,300
That's right.

570
00:24:12,033 --> 00:24:12,967
Is that all?

571
00:24:14,633 --> 00:24:16,633
(Furious)
The conversation ended
because you didn't pick up what I was saying.

572
00:24:16,633 --> 00:24:17,800
He's angry. XINLONG's angry.

573
00:24:17,800 --> 00:24:18,467
Sorry.

574
00:24:18,467 --> 00:24:20,367
(Hugging)

575
00:24:20,367 --> 00:24:24,733
(Feeling better with some fruit as a treat)

576
00:24:25,567 --> 00:24:27,233
(Mm♥)

577
00:24:27,233 --> 00:24:28,367
(Self-plane)

578
00:24:28,367 --> 00:24:29,500
(Nom)

579
00:24:29,500 --> 00:24:31,100
(The meal ended with the strawberry dance)

580
00:24:31,100 --> 00:24:33,500
(CHINYANGZ's fun day is over)

581
00:24:33,500 --> 00:24:34,667
We enjoyed it fully!

582
00:24:34,667 --> 00:24:35,967
We had so much fun too!

583
00:24:35,967 --> 00:24:37,200
I was so happy!

584
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:39,433
But sadly, the other members aren't here.

585
00:24:39,433 --> 00:24:41,533
It's just the three of us.

586
00:24:41,533 --> 00:24:42,767
That's the only thing I'm bummed about.

587
00:24:42,767 --> 00:24:45,100
Even though today was such a happy day,

588
00:24:45,100 --> 00:24:45,767
it's a little disappointing.

589
00:24:45,767 --> 00:24:46,700
(Holding back laughter)

590
00:24:46,700 --> 00:24:47,900
(Haha)

591
00:24:47,900 --> 00:24:50,567
(Hahahaha)

592
00:24:50,567 --> 00:24:52,333
A nice comment!

593
00:24:52,333 --> 00:24:53,633
Okay, this has been!

594
00:24:53,633 --> 00:24:55,833
ALPHA DRIVE ONE.

595
00:24:55,833 --> 00:24:57,467
Bye bye~

